COG Advisor 
Age: 27 yrs 
Race: Human 
Class: Sorcerer 
Rank: Adept 

![Vo Blackbrook.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Vo is a charmer! When he talks women and men alike have been known to swoon, which is why being the Guild Advisor was an obvious choice. Vo talks a big game and can back it up with his natural magical talent. Though he seems to be the Guild Casanova he found a soft spot in his heart for an abandoned Opossum-folk during one of his Quests. He brought her back and raised her with the Guild and taught her magic just like him. He is a Proud Papa and cannot imagine any harm befalling his precious Spreelee. There was once a time he nearly drowned a member for uttering an insult towards his baby girl, of course the man was saved but was banned as COG does not condone hate towards any race. You can often find Vo in the tavern trying to convince Fae to give him a chance at a date.
